      <description>Folksinger Jean Ritchie performs the Appalachian tune &amp;ldquo;Shady Grove,&amp;rdquo; a traditional song she learned from her family. Then she performs &amp;ldquo;Bandyrowe,&amp;rdquo; a song for which she made up verses to help get her two sons to sleep when they were very young. Ritchie accompanies herself on the lap dulcimer.</description>
